tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Má»¥c lá»¥c:&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"#1\">1. Chá»n nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng nÆ°á»›ng b&aacute;nh Ä‘&uacute;ng chuáº©n gi&uacute;p vá» b&aacute;nh má»m v&agrave; Ä‘áº¹p hÆ¡n</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"#2\">2. Chá»n Ä‘&uacute;ng loáº¡i bá»™t Ä‘á»ƒ l&agrave;m vá» b&aacute;nh&nbsp;trung thu xá»‘p dáº»o</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"#3\">3. C&aacute;ch s&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n Ä‘&uacute;ng chuáº©n Ä‘á»ƒ&nbsp;Ä‘áº£m báº£o Ä‘á»™ ngon v&agrave; thá»i gian báº£o quáº£n</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"#4\">4. Ká»¹ thuáº­t bá»c b&aacute;nh, náº·n b&aacute;nh&nbsp;v&agrave; v&agrave;o khu&ocirc;n Ä‘&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch&nbsp;</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"#5\">5. Chá»n l&ograve; nÆ°á»›ng b&aacute;nh Trung thu ph&ugrave; há»£p v&agrave; nÆ°á»›ng b&aacute;nh Ä‘&uacute;ng quy tr&igrave;nh</a></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><em><img alt=\"BÃ­ quyáº¿t lÃ m bÃ¡nh Trung thu nÆ°á»›ng thÆ¡m ngon vá»›i lÃ² nÆ°á»›ng Capri\" src=\"http://capri.vn/upload/files/bi-quyet-lam-banh-trung-thu-nuong-thom-ngon-voi-lo-nuong-cr-602m.jpg\" style=\"height:393px; width:750px\" /></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><a id=\"1\" name=\"1\"></a>1. Chá»n nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng nÆ°á»›ng b&aacute;nh Ä‘&uacute;ng chuáº©n gi&uacute;p vá» b&aacute;nh má»m v&agrave; Ä‘áº¹p hÆ¡n</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">NÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng l&agrave; th&agrave;nh pháº§n quan trá»ng nháº¥t trong b&aacute;nh Trung Thu nÆ°á»›ng.&nbsp;NÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng b&aacute;nh nÆ°á»›c c&oacute; t&aacute;c dá»¥ng l&agrave;m cháº¥t lá»ng x&uacute;c t&aacute;c trong qu&aacu