nhÆ° cháº¥t lÆ°á»£ng cá»§a b&aacute;nh.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- Máº¡ch nha cÅ©ng l&agrave; má»™t yáº¿u tá»‘ gi&uacute;p nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng b&aacute;nh nÆ°á»›ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c thÆ¡m ngon.&nbsp;Máº¡ch nha Ä‘&oacute;ng vai tr&ograve;&nbsp;l&agrave;m má»m v&agrave; s&aacute;nh nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng. Náº¿u sá»­ dá»¥ng máº¡ch nha, báº¡n n&ecirc;n mua máº¡ch nha dáº¡ng sá»‡t, trong suá»‘t.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><img alt=\"BÃ­ quyáº¿t náº¥u nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng lÃ m bÃ¡nh trung thu\" src=\"http://capri.vn/upload/files/bi-quyet-nau-nuoc-duong-lam-banh-trung-thu.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em><u><strong>B&iacute; quyáº¿t náº¥u nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng báº¥t báº¡i sau 2 tuáº§n l&agrave; c&oacute; thá»ƒ sá»­ dá»¥ng</strong></u></em></span></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>**Nguy&ecirc;n liá»‡u:</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- 500g Ä‘Æ°á»ng n&acirc;u (n&ecirc;n sá»­ dá»¥ng Ä‘Æ°á»ng n&acirc;u H&agrave;n Quá»‘c sáº½ thÆ¡m hÆ¡n).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- 500g Ä‘Æ°á»ng c&aacute;t tráº¯ng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- 600 ml nÆ°á»›c lá»c.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- 1 tr&aacute;i chanh v&agrave;ng hoáº·c 500g dá»©a (thÆ¡m).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- 30 ml máº¡ch nha.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>**C&aacute;ch náº¥u:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>- BÆ°á»›c 1:&nbsp;</strong>Äun s&ocirc;i 600 ml nÆ°á»›c trong 1 c&aacute;i ná»“i tá»›i khi s&ocirc;i. Láº¥y 1 c&aacute;i ná»“i kh&aacute;c trá»™n Ä‘á»u 2 loáº¡i Ä‘Æ°á»ng láº¡i vá»›i nhau. Sau Ä‘&oacute; tá»« tá»« cháº¿ nÆ°á»›c s&ocirc;i v&agrave;o ná»“i Ä‘Æ°á»ng v&agrave; khuáº¥y Ä‘á»u cho Ä‘Æ°á»ng tan háº¿t.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>- BÆ°á»›c 2</strong>: Báº¯t ná»“i nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng l&ecirc;n báº¿p náº¥u á»Ÿ lá»­a lá»›n tá»›i khi s&ocirc;i lÄƒn tÄƒn, táº¡o bá»t tráº¯ng th&igrave; háº¡ lá»­a xuá»‘ng vá»«a, há»›t bá»t.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>- BÆ°á»›c 3</strong>: Cho nÆ°á»›c cá»‘t chanh v&agrave;ng v&agrave;o (khoáº£ng 70 ml), náº¿u d&ugrave;ng thÆ¡m th&igrave; báº¡n cÅ©ng n&ecirc;n cho khoáº£ng 15 ml nÆ°á»›c chanh v&agrave;o náº¥u liu riu trong khoáº£ng 60 ph&uacute;t. NÆ°á»›c chanh sáº½ gi&uacute;p cho nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng cá»§a báº¡n kh&ocirc;ng bá»‹ káº¿t tinh.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>- BÆ°á»›c 4</strong>: Tiáº¿p Ä‘&oacute; má»›i cho vá» chanh v&agrave;ng (náº¿u náº¥u báº±ng chanh) hoáº·c thÆ¡m (náº¿u náº¥u báº±ng thÆ¡m) v&agrave;o náº¥u th&ecirc;m 30 ph&uacute;t ná»¯a.&nbsp;<strong>Tuyá»‡t Ä‘á»‘i kh&ocirc;ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c khuáº¥y, quáº­y nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng trong giai Ä‘oáº¡n n&agrave;y</strong>. Sau Ä‘&oacute; cho th&ecirc;m máº¡ch nha v&agrave;o.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h4><u><em><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>C&aacute;ch thá»­ nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng Ä‘áº¡t chuáº©n:</strong></span></em></u></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- Th&ocirc;ng thÆ°á»ng vá»›i 600 ml nÆ°á»›c v&agrave; 1 kg Ä‘Æ°á»ng náº¥u ra Ä‘Æ°á»£c 1.1 kg - 1.2 kg nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng l&agrave; Ä‘áº¡t chuáº©n.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- Khoáº£ng 15 ph&uacute;t sau khi cho máº¡ch nha, báº¡n kiá»ƒm tra Ä‘á»™ Ä‘áº¡t cá»§a nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng báº±ng c&aacute;ch nhá» thá»­ 1 giá»t nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng v&agrave;o 1 chiáº¿c Ä‘Ä©a pháº³ng, trong v&agrave;i gi&acirc;y Ä‘áº§u ti&ecirc;n rá»“i ngÆ°ng háº³n, giá»t nÆ°á»›c váº«n giá»¯ Ä‘Æ°á»£c h&igrave;nh tr&ograve;n l&agrave; Ä‘áº¡t.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- Má»™t c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c, chuáº©n bá»‹ má»™t ch&eacute;n nÆ°á»›c, nhá» v&agrave;o giá»t nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng v&agrave;o, náº¿u nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng láº¯ng xuá»‘ng, loang nháº¹ ra th&agrave;nh h&igrave;nh tr&ograve;n má»™t ch&uacute;t rá»“i ngÆ°ng, kh&ocirc;ng h&ograve;a tan l&agrave; Ä‘&atilde; Ä‘áº¡t. C&ograve;n náº¿u nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng nhá» xuá»‘ng láº­p tá»©c tan v&agrave;o nÆ°á»›c l&agrave; náº¥u chÆ°a tá»›i, cáº§n náº¥u th&ecirc;m. Náº¿u nÆ°á»›c Ä‘Æ°á»ng nhá» xuá»‘ng v&oacute;n cá»¥c l&agrave; Ä‘&atilde; náº¥u qu&aacute; l&acirc;u, c&aacute;ch chá»¯a l&agrave; th&ecirc;m má»™t &iacute;t nÆ°á»›c s&ocirc;i v&agrave;o v&agrave; Ä‘un tiáº¿p sau Ä‘&oacute; thá»­ láº¡i xem Ä‘áº¡t chÆ°a.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><a id=\"2\" name=\"2\"></a>2. Chá»n Ä‘&uacute;ng loáº¡i bá»™t Ä‘á»ƒ l&agrave;m vá» b&aacute;nh&nbsp;trung thu xá»‘p dáº»o</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Äá»™ ngon cá»§a b&aacute;nh phá»¥ thuá»™c ráº¥t nhiá»u v&agrave;o loáº¡i bá»™t m&agrave; báº¡n sá»­ dá»¥ng Ä‘á»ƒ l&agrave;m vá» b&aacute;nh.&nbsp;C&oacute; nhá»¯ng loáº¡i bá»™t th&ocirc;ng dá»¥ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c nhiá»u ngÆ°á»i d&ugrave;ng nhÆ° bá»™t b&aacute;nh m&igrave; sá»‘ 13, bá»™t b&aacute;nh ngá»t, bá»™t m&igrave; Ä‘a dá»¥ng (Meizan, T&aacute;o Ä‘á», Sanh K&yacute;...), bá»™t b&aacute;nh trung thu pha sáºµn,...Nhá»¯ng loáº¡i bá»™t kh&aacute;c nhau sáº½ l&agrave;m ra vá» b&aacute;nh trung thu c&oacute; cháº¥t lÆ°á»£ng kh&aacute;c nhau.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Bá»™t b&aacute;nh m&igrave; (<strong>bá»™t m&igrave; sá»‘ 13</strong>) sáº½ cho ra vá» b&aacute;nh cháº¯c tay, cá»©ng c&aacute;p nhÆ°ng kh&aacute; kh&ocirc;.&nbsp;Bá»™t b&aacute;nh ngá»t&nbsp;(<strong>bá»™t m&igrave; sá»‘ 8</strong>) v&agrave; bá»™t m&igrave; Ä‘a dá»¥ng&nbsp;(<strong>bá»™t m&igrave; sá»‘ 11</strong>) láº¡i cho ra vá» b&aacute;nh c&oacute; Ä‘á»™ má»m dáº»o hÆ¡n.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><img alt=\"CÃ¡c loáº¡i bá»™t lÃ m bÃ¡nh trung thu dáº»o ngon\" src=\"http://capri.vn