b&ecirc;n trong báº¿p.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Tr&ecirc;n Ä‘&acirc;y l&agrave; nhá»¯ng lÆ°u &yacute; chung khi sá»­ dá»¥ng báº¿p Ä‘iá»‡n tá»« CR-828KT cÅ©ng nhÆ° c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng báº¿p Ä‘iá»‡n tá»« kh&aacute;c cá»§a Capri sao cho an to&agrave;n, hiá»‡u quáº£. Má»i kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng khi mua h&agrave;ng cá»§a Capri Ä‘á»u Ä‘Æ°á»£c&nbsp;há»— trá»£ láº¯p Ä‘áº·t v&agrave; hÆ°á»›ng dáº«n sá»­ dá»¥ng chu Ä‘&aacute;o Ä‘&uacute;ng vá»›i phÆ°Æ¡ng ch&acirc;m hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng cá»§a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i Ä‘&oacute; l&agrave; &quot;Gi&aacute; trá»‹ bá»n vá»¯ng- Phá»¥c vá»¥ táº­n t&acirc;m&quot;, nháº±m táº¡o sá»± h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng nháº¥t cho ngÆ°á»i ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng. Äá»ƒ nháº­n Ä‘Æ°á»£c nhá»¯ng Æ°u Ä‘&atilde;i tá»‘t nháº¥t c&ugrave;ng sáº£n pháº©m ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng,&nbsp;cháº¥t lÆ°á»£ng,&nbsp;qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng h&atilde;y&nbsp;Ä‘áº¿n Ä‘&uacute;ng Ä‘á»‹a chá»‰ showroom, Ä‘áº¡i l&yacute; v&agrave; c&aacute;c cá»­a h&agrave;ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c á»§y quyá»n ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng cá»§a Capri.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"><u><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Má»i chi tiáº¿t xin vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n há»‡:&nbsp;</strong></span></u></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- Website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.capri.vn\">www.capri.vn&nbsp;</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">- Fanpage:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bepCapri\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bepCapri&nbsp;</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Hoáº·c qua hotline:&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#ff0000\"><strong>0932 939 039</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><em><strong><span style=\"color:#000099\">THIáº¾T Bá»Š NH&Agrave; Báº¾P CAO Cáº¤P CH&Acirc;U &Acirc;U CAPRI </span>-&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#ff0000\">&ldquo;GI&Aacute; TRá»Š Bá»€N Vá»®NG - PHá»¤C Vá»¤ Táº¬N T&Acirc;M&rdquo;</span></strong></em></s